---
title: Feta, Leek and Kale Pie (v) with Mushrooms and a Crispy Panko Topping
description: Today's recipe owes something to the delicious Greek spinach-and-feta pies known as 'spanakopita' but we've given it a British twist. Instead of spinach we're using leek and kale, and a hotpot-style potato topping has replaced the filo pastry. It's an Anglo-Hellenic hybrid! We hope you enjoy it as much as we do.
